{"tid":748448,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"白宮經濟顧問預告將推出更多稅改","createTime":"2018-07-19T08:26:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-19T13:44:11.000Z","uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ba4211c0fea1f8ae3d236b261d5a18b8be244916","tid":748448,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T08:26:58.000Z","msg":"白宮經濟顧問預告將推出更多稅改<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-news/NOW.884652/2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.aastocks.com%2Ftc%2Fstocks%2Fnews%2Faafn-news%2FNOW.884652%2F2&d=MPR8sQOOPtB75xu9CZ45TdZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=c1616ea1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-news/NOW.884652/2</a><br />\n<br />\n美國白宮首席經濟顧問庫德洛接受《CNBC》訪問表示，美國經濟增長將達3%，顯著高於過去10年水平，在一兩個季度可達4%，意味百萬計民眾有工作。他指政府正考慮更多稅改，可能有稅改2.0、3.0及4.0版本。<br />\n<br />\n庫德洛又指，小孩及千禧一代等未經歷長期及全面的經濟繁榮，美國已有逾20年未經歷經濟強勁。美國政府透過減稅、增加開支及減少監管，試圖令美國經濟走出金融海嘯後的「增長衰退」。(fc/ca)"},{"pid":"540a9c2e256b5c79e3cb868165503682c8157078","tid":748448,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T08:32:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dd81b32f56f0f5333a55b82860323ece0c5a682","tid":748448,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T09:02:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56be5ecfaaa69bacad47d2794ab6d6fe52756db6","tid":748448,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T13:44:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomor